Privacy Policy for Plane Removel

Effective Date: December 24, 2025
We respect your privacy and are committed to protecting your personal information when you use our app Plane Removel. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and protect your data.

1. Information We Collect
Personal Information: The app does not collect personal information such as your name or email unless you voluntarily provide it.
Usage Data: We may collect non-personal information such as gameplay data (levels played, scores, settings) to improve your experience.
Device Information: Non-personal device data such as device type, operating system, and performance metrics may be collected for analytics purposes.

2. How We Use Information
To improve and enhance the game experience.
To display advertisements (such as Unity Ads) within the app.
To troubleshoot issues and analyze app performance.

3. Advertisements
Our app may display ads from third-party ad networks (e.g., Unity Ads).
These ads may use cookies or similar technologies to collect information about your interaction with the ads.
We do not share your personal information with advertisers. Only general non-personal information may be used by ad networks.

4. Data Protection
We use appropriate technical measures to protect your information from unauthorized access, alteration, or deletion.

5. Third-Party Links
The app may contain links to external websites or services.
We are not responsible for the privacy practices of these third-party websites or services.

6. Changes to This Privacy Policy
We reserve the right to update this Privacy Policy at any time.
Users will be notified of any significant changes by updating this page.

7. Contact Us
If you have any questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at:
Email: ksa.trq.ksa@gmail.com
